Class BSXModule

                    +--modules.BSXModule
public class BSXModule
extends java.awt.Panel
implements Module

The ultimate BSX module implements most of the common used BSX controll sequences.

Features:

  • a Statemachine to parse the Strings passed by the telnet
  • a own package named bsx, for Window and Polygon handling terrible english because my native language is german
TODO:
  • more BSX Sequences
  • Documentaion

Author:
Thomas Kriegelstein
